      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_68f13d69-5228-4e68-a18a-fac798436d66",
      "del:text": "I agree with <MENTION>"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_65a00036-6405-44c5-9b95-f32a72582602",
      "del:text": "'It''s asking you to test the rule . Would it not prove that the rule is tested if the <CARD> turns up a vowel ?'"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_2789bff4-aecc-41f1-834c-30b56b88b73d",
      "del:text": "the test is all cards with a vowel"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_e33cfda1-23e5-405d-bc75-5eae97cb509e",
      "del:text": "'Couldn''t the <CARD> just as easily have turned up a consonant ? In which case , the <CARD> is not necessary to prove the rule ?'"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_27bb5149-af74-4602-8410-88693c16396e",
      "del:text": "Good point ."
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_de4a9996-38a8-4a93-b7cd-2ac7ac9b7894",
      "del:text": "again - <MENTION> - I agree"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_337d30ae-a678-4cf0-ae59-10266e5d919b",
      "del:text": "But would it not strengthen the correlation if we did find a vowel ?"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_8a7ce559-d148-427d-863b-6194bac8c2b2",
      "del:text": "if <CARD> has an even number on the other side the rule is proven"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_1eb0aa58-a43b-48ae-a22c-9895807600a7",
      "del:text": "Would turning over the <CARD> not be useful for testing ?"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_e1170981-a59e-49d2-909e-30f6d76f934c",
      "del:text": "'It might help , but if we didn''t find a vowel it would hurt the rule .'"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_87439ea5-f872-4c76-86bc-7956a638cde7",
      "del:text": "It would , but it does seem like that would be necessary for a proper test ."
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_c3d9c323-cc3c-4e0e-9e80-0f1bb2ad962b",
      "del:text": "The question in the task implies that you only need one card to prove the rule ."
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_ba55e79f-049d-4e0b-9c39-56d068532aec",
      "del:text": "While it does , it says most players get it wrong . The assumption then would be that the task is more complex than that ."
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_a6945464-b63f-410a-8c5a-814068a6ae7f",
      "del:text": "if you want to turn a second card - turn <CARD> - if <CARD> has a vowel on the other side the rule is also proven"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_607826ac-278f-4bbe-8ab9-fa67db138de5",
      "del:text": "you turn ONLY the cards needed"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_0b41312c-6dc1-4aa4-938e-fa55c4e584f9",
      "del:text": "'Agree with <MENTION> . You don''t \" need \" to turn over the <CARD> to prove the rule .'"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_c4f9c485-1104-4fcf-bba9-87e107ed6a4f",
      "del:text": "Does <CARD> coming up even really prove it if other cards could show something different ?"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_fda3ceb5-cb51-4fb1-91e2-04a76ac776f7",
      "del:text": "ONLY is key"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_c090f57f-72e9-4dac-8f28-819905385942",
      "del:text": "'no it''s a logical exclusion'"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_d83c3eca-1dfb-485c-8e7f-b6b20f9c86f1",
      "del:text": "so what do we agree to ?"
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_5eda9c19-b304-4f38-b885-1cf980456b4f",
      "del:text": "I vote \" <CARD> \" only ."
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_181d3792-e1fb-47b2-b1cf-8614c87ddf06",
      "del:text": "I vote <CARD> only"
    }
  ]
